The University's Spirit and the Spirit of the Times - Official website
The so-called university spirit refers to the long-term accumulation of a university in the development process of a series of running ideas and the pursuit of value, is the soul of the university.
From ancient times to the present day, the university spirit has been vital to the development of politics, economy, culture, science and technology, society, and even the progress of a nation.
Since the birth of the world's first university in the modern sense, the university has assumed a unique mission different from other social organizations. For our university, it arose in the autumn of national danger, its spirit is deeply influenced by traditional culture and the changes of the times, advocating the value idea of "Ming Dynasty, Jizei, Shu Qi Jiping" and the patriotism of "Get up to study strong country".
At present, the trend of informationization and internationalization of higher education is becoming increasingly evident, and the global competition in education, science and technology, and talents is intensifying. As an important “supply side,” higher education is facing unprecedented opportunities and challenges in its structural reform.
In particular, the proposal of the "Overall Programme for Promoting the Construction of World-Class Universities and First-Class Subjects" demonstrates the confidence and determination of our country to move forward from a high-education country to a high-education country, and at the same time puts forward higher and more up-to-date requirements for the development of universities.
How can we accelerate the construction of a number of world-class universities and a number of world-class subjects in a shorter period of time and achieve the “bend-over”?
In addition to firm objective self-confidence, path self-confidence, and ability self-confidence, universities should also give full play to three advantages: first, a backward advantage, by continuously introducing outstanding academic talents overseas, learning from the advanced experience of world-class universities, and achieving a remarkable improvement in academic standards and the quality of running schools; second, a cultural advantage, inheriting the wisdom connotation of Chinese civilization accumulated over five thousand years, and promoting the development of excellent traditional culture, thereby consolidating strength, shaping brands, and raising the image; and third, a institutional advantage, giving full play to the institutional superiority of the socialist country, strengthening the objective drive, pooling consensus, and optimizing resource allocation, so as to provide sustainable and solid guarantees for schools to accelerate
In particular, we must realize that it is impossible to build a world-class university on a one-sided basis, and each school must show its individuality and characteristics while playing an advantage.
The characteristics of running schools should not only have the Chinese characteristics, but also embody their own unique goals, running traditions and resource endowments.
As far as Zhejiang University is concerned, we have focused on highlighting three features in running our school: firstly, we have highlighted the characteristics of innovative entrepreneurial talent cultivation, built an integrated environment for the integration of science, education and enterprises, and formed a whole-chain entrepreneurial education ecosystem; secondly, we have highlighted the characteristics of cross-disciplinary convergence, promoted the optimization and adjustment of the discipline system, and built an institutional environment for cross-disciplinary interchange, actively nurtured cross-emerging disciplines and landmark cross-cutting achievements; and thirdly, we have highlighted the characteristics of running our school and social services, conducted deep international exchange and cooperation, and accelerated the formation of a pan-Zhejiang system for cooperation in science and research.
In this process, it is especially important to always stick to the university spirit, so that the university spirit resonates with the spirit of the times.
For Zhejiang University, the newest system of expression of Zhejiang University’s spirit is founded on the principle of “innovation,” the shared values of “ diligence, virtue, discernment, and faithfulness,” and “the Haina River, enlightenment, virtue, pioneering people, and our nation.”
This is an important guarantee that the school adheres to the correct direction of running the school, continuously accumulates a high level of culture and cohesive spiritual strength, and has rich connotation and far-reaching significance.
Among them, "Hina River" emphasizes the spirit of openness and inclusiveness, embodied in the heart of "the world's talents for me to use" and expressed as the high-quality idea of drawing on the world-famous schools to run and educate people; "Enlightenment and good morality" emphasizes the spirit of seeking truth and goodness, which means that the university, while pursuing the truth, should be more subject to the cultivation of virtue and personality; "Open-minded people" emphasizes the spirit of reform and innovation, which includes the search for new knowledge, scientific research and innovation, but also expressed as reform development and revolution; "Tree our nation" emphasizes the spirit of patriotic devotion, saying that the university should always be honored and humiliated with the fate of the nation.
This series of spiritual ideas and value pursuit is the soul of Zhejiang University's 120 years of running.
“He who is wise hears in silence, and he who is wise sees in the unseen.”
China's universities and colleges should further build on the overall development of socialism with Chinese characteristics, grasp the historical orientation of higher education and its historical mission, and accelerate the construction of world-class universities.
At the same time, we must uphold humanistic concern and independence, so that the spirit of the university, the spirit of the times and the spirit of the nation can be stirred up, thus providing an inexhaustible impetus for the realization of the nation's wealth and strength, the revival of the nation, and the realization of the common ideal of mankind.
