Last night, the head of publicity for the downtown branch of Hangzhou Public Security Bureau confirmed to reporters in Xinjing that the police confirmed that the girl raised money for her sister to make such an outrageous move, but the behavior is not worth promoting, the girl has left the local police station yesterday after being warned.
