Xinhua News Agency (Xinhua News Agency) has learned from the Education Department of Guangxi Zhuang Autonomous Region on May 19 that universities in Guangxi will implement a flexible education system in the future, relaxing the period for university students to leave school, the period for students to leave school to start a business can be extended from two to five years on the basis of the original education system, and the period for students to leave school to start a business can be regarded as the time for practical education.
